        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1650704128
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, found the bug. When you add <code>local</code> then it accidentally turns off the checks that there are no attributes or modifiers. (And no, <code>priority</code> is meant to raise an error along with everything else.)</p>",
